OL,3,CCompensation for pollack fishers hit
OL,4,Cby zero catch quota
OL,6,FPollack fishers in Devon and Cornwall
OL,7,Fwho have been hit by a zero catch
OL,8,Flimit will receive compensation, the
OL,9,Fgovernment has announced.
OL,11,FThe Environment Secretary said
OL,12,Falthough fishermen were warned of a
OL,13,Fpossible quota reduction, they had not
OL,14,Fbeen adequately prepared for it to
OL,15,Ffall to zero.
OL,17,FAround 50 vessel owners who rely on
OL,18,Fpollack for at least 30% of their
OL,19,Fearnings will be directly compensated
OL,20,Ffor half of their lost income.
