OL,3,CCompensation for pollack fishers hit
OL,4,Cby zero catch quota
OL,6,FSteve Barclay MP said: "I fully
OL,7,Frecognise the impact that the bycatch-
OL,8,Fonly advice has had on pollack fishers
OL,9,Fin the South West and have therefore
OL,10,Facted to provide support to those most
OL,11,Faffected.
OL,13,F"The compensation scheme will support
OL,14,Fthese hardworking fishers and provide
OL,15,Fthem with an opportunity to move away
OL,16,Ffrom a reliance on the pollack fishery
OL,17,Fas we work to further support the
OL,18,Frecovery of the stock."
