OL,6,FIn a ministerial direction to his
OL,7,Fdepartment, the environment secretary
OL,8,Falso warned "DEFRA needs to learn
OL,9,Flessons from this case".
OL,11,FHe also added "improvement in
OL,12,Fcommunications around the management
OL,13,Fof stocks in future, to prevent the
OL,14,Findustry being caught by surprise, as
OL,15,Fin this case, can further mitigate
OL,16,Fthis."
